# [Pi-hole installation on home network]

Date: [06/2026]
Status: [completed]

---

## Overview

Pi-hole is an open source, self-hosted DNS sinkhole that can be installed on a raspberry pi device. Pi-hole blocks advertisements and trackers network-wide through DNS query management. 
Pi-hole is configured with a static IP for consistent DNS resolutions and provides an administrator dashboard for real time monitoring, block statistics, and other pertinent settings.

